<%- include('./partials/navigation.ejs') %>
<div class="application-description">
    <h4 class="application-guideliness">Application Guidelines</h4>
    The application's pupose is to provide users with the possibility of reporting daily behavior activities such as:
    <ul class="activities-list">
        <li>Sleep duration and sleep quality</li>
        <li>Time spent on sports and exercise</li>
        <li>Time spent studying</li>
        <li>Regularity and quality of eating</li>
        <li>Generic mood</li>
    </ul>
    The reporting is performed in two periods every day, morning and evening reports (check the Reporting Tab). </br>
    Furthermore, the users are able to see reports on a weekly or monthly period of their activity (check the Summary Tab). 
</div>
<div class="users-trends">
    <h4>Current Users Generic Mood Trends</h4>
    <div class="morning-trend">
        <div class="row morning-trend-yesterday">
            Yesterday generic morning mood: <%= moodSummaryYesterday.morning_mood_avg %> out of 5.00
        </div>
        <div class="row morning-trend-today">
            Today generic morning mood: <%= moodSummaryToday.morning_mood_avg %> out of 5.00
        </div>
        <% if (moodSummaryYesterday.morning_mood_avg > moodSummaryToday.morning_mood_avg) { %>
            <div class="decreasing-trend">
                Today morning seems like a harsh day. Please, take care!
            </div>
        <% } else { %>
            <div class="increasing-trend">
                Today morning looks absolutely lovely. Have an awesome day!
            </div>
        <% } %>
    </div>
    <div class="evening-trend">
        <div class="row evening-trend-yesterday">
            Yesterday generic evening mood: <%= moodSummaryYesterday.evening_mood_avg %>  out of 5.00
        </div>
        <div class="row evening-trend-today">
            Today generic evening mood: <%= moodSummaryToday.evening_mood_avg %>  out of 5.00
        </div>
        <% if (moodSummaryYesterday.evening_mood_avg > moodSummaryToday.evening_mood_avg) { %>
            <div class="decreasing-trend">
                Today evening seems rather unpleasent. Please, avoid making bad decision!
            </div>
        <% } else { %>
            <div class="increasing-trend">
                Today evening looks absolutely lovely. Have an awesome night-out!
            </div>
        <% } %>
    </div>
</div>
